channel.title: What should I name my new server
channel.description:
Actually saw a post on this so hopes its allowed in this section but me and my bro cant think of a name for are server. Are first one was called Dwarfscape but we dont really want to carry on the name or the theme. Any kind of name would be pretty good. Dont really want a theme name or a name thats already been used. Like we werething of some but there not very good
-Balsawood scape -uggscape -boBscape -Odyssey'scape
If you like any of those we could use those or if you want to come up with your own.
